23 February 2015Economic Sectors, Employment and Infrastructure Development Cluster chaired by minister of Rural Development and Land Reform, Gugile Nkwinti will hold a media briefing on the implementation of the Government Programme of Action post State of the Nation Address 2015.Media briefing will be held as follows:Date: Tuesday, 24 February 2015 Time: 10h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street in Parliament, Cape Town with a video link up to Tshedimosetso House (DOC), Pretoria.RSVPs: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 082 440 5676 Email: ireen@doc.gov.zaSibusiso Banda (Cape Town) Cell: 076 456 1821 Email: sibusisob@doc,gov.zaEnquiries: Nikelwa Tengimfene (Economic Sectors, Employment and Infrastructure Development Cluster Supervisor) Cell: 082 574 5495Issued by Department of Communications (DoC)